| Entity | Aciklama | Temel Propertyler |
|--------|----------|-------------------|
| Product | Urun master | Name, Description, Brand, Category, Images[], SEO |
| Variant | Urun varyanti | SKU, Price, Stock, Attributes (color, size), Weight |
| Category | Urun kategorisi | Name, ParentId, Slug, Image, IsActive |
| Cart | Sepet | UserId, Items[], TotalAmount, CouponCode |
| CartItem | Sepet kalemi | VariantId, Quantity, UnitPrice |
| Order | Siparis | OrderNumber, CustomerId, Status, Items[], Totals |
| OrderItem | Siparis kalemi | VariantId, Qty, UnitPrice, Discount, Tax |
| Payment | Odeme | OrderId, Method, Amount, Status, TransactionId |
| Shipment | Kargo | OrderId, CarrierId, TrackingNo, Status |
| Return | Iade | OrderId, Items[], Reason, Status, RefundAmount |
| Customer | Musteri | Name, Email, Phone, Addresses[], OrderHistory |
| Address | Adres | Type (billing/shipping), City, District, Line1, Zip |
| Coupon | Kupon | Code, Type (percent/fixed), Value, MinOrder, ExpiryDate |
| Campaign | Kampanya | Name, Type, Rules[], StartDate, EndDate |
| Review | Degerlendirme | ProductId, UserId, Rating (1-5), Comment, Images[] |
| Wishlist | Favori listesi | UserId, ProductIds[] |

