## Is Kurallari

### Fiyat Hesaplama
```
Base Price (Variant.Price)
  - Product Discount (urun indirimi)
  - Campaign Discount (kampanya)
  - Coupon Discount (kupon kodu)
  = Net Price
  + Tax (KDV: %1, %10, %20 — urun kategorisine gore)
  + Shipping Fee
  = Total Amount

Kurallar:
├── Indirimler urunun BASE price'i uzerinden hesaplanir
├── Kampanya + kupon AYNI ANDA uygulanabilir (config'e bagli)
├── Minimum siparis tutari kontrolu (kupon icin)
├── Maximum indirim limiti (kupon icin)
├── Negatif tutar OLMAZ — min 0.01 TL
```

### Stok Rezervasyonu
```
Sepete eklendi -> Soft reserve (15 dk, configurable)
Odeme basladi -> Hard reserve (30 dk)
Odeme basarili -> Committed (stoktan dus)
Odeme basarisiz -> Release reserve
Sepet timeout -> Release reserve

KURAL: Stok gosterimi = Available - Reserved
KURAL: Overselling YASAK (race condition icin distributed lock)
```

### Kupon Kurallari
```
├── Tip: Yuzde (%) veya sabit tutar (TL)
├── Min siparis: kuponun gecerli olmasi icin min tutar
├── Max indirim: yuzdelik kuponlarda tavan
├── Kullanim limiti: toplam kullanim + kisi basi kullanim
├── Gecerlilik: baslangic-bitis tarihi
├── Urun/kategori kisitlamasi: sadece belirli urunlerde
├── Ilk siparis kuponu: sadece yeni musteriler
├── Combinable: baska kuponlarla birlesebilir mi?
```

## Status Akislari

### Order Lifecycle
```
Draft -> PendingPayment -> Paid -> Processing -> Picking
  -> Packed -> Shipped -> Delivered -> Completed
  -> Cancelled (PendingPayment veya Paid'de mumkun)
  -> PartiallyShipped (multi-parcel)
  -> ReturnRequested -> ReturnReceived -> Refunded
```

### Payment Lifecycle
```
Initiated -> Processing -> Succeeded -> (Refunded)
  -> Failed -> Retry (max 3)
  -> Cancelled
  -> PartialRefund
```

### Return Lifecycle
```
Requested -> Approved -> CargoLabelSent -> InTransit
  -> Received -> Inspected -> Refunded
  -> Rejected (sartlara uymayan)
  -> PartialRefund (kismi iade)
```

## KPI'lar
| KPI | Formul | Hedef |
|-----|--------|-------|
| Conversion Rate | Siparis / Ziyaretci | > %2-3 |
| Cart Abandon Rate | Terk edilen / Toplam sepet | < %70 |
| Average Order Value | Toplam gelir / Siparis sayisi | Artis trendi |
| Customer Acquisition Cost | Pazarlama / Yeni musteri | Azalis trendi |
| Customer Lifetime Value | Ort. siparis x Ort. siparis sayisi | Artis trendi |
| Return Rate | Iade / Toplam siparis | < %10 |
| Net Promoter Score | Promoter - Detractor | > 50 |
| First Response Time | CS ilk yanit suresi | < 2 saat |
